{"tid":8176,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［書蟲召喚］一人一本好書推介","createTime":"2016-11-28T07:56:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-08T07:45:41.000Z","uid":9943,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cc09f209e20067e8fbc2c102c114cd49e24c68fe","tid":8176,"uid":9943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T07:56:11.000Z","msg":"其實係我想搵啲英文書放入kindle度睇<br />\n中文書而家搵到的ebook都係經典類，想睇新書我直接買實體書算了<br />\n但英文可以在amazon買<br />\n所以想搵同好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n分享一下而家睇緊的<br />\n叫A Butler's Guide To Table Manners，作者係Nicholas Clayton，會詳細講解fine dining的dos and don'ts，英式串嘴同幽默，唔悶又學到野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大家又有無好介紹？"},{"pid":"6e3c0c185d51c8fadc8dc67e3a6c7946b3184272","tid":8176,"uid":9943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T11:19:16.000Z","msg":"認真post無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12716f6f4641c046bb1f8a295ab44f8f61e20af2","tid":8176,"uid":1495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T12:18:34.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e80cb5331859d361c070f2bac35072d01251ade","tid":8176,"uid":19978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T12:30:46.000Z","msg":"學術定悠閒？"},{"pid":"a17954119743eb6b8cb8ef76011fbe6713ee4799","tid":8176,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-05T14:22:42.000Z","msg":"1984"},{"pid":"57acd6e268c1ed01b4eea0dc6a70c718b48c2aa5","tid":8176,"uid":9943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T14:11:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>學術定悠閒？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n原來有人應 但我完全唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw多謝你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咩都好 我睇書雜得黎唔係特別有心機睇學術<br />\n但如果只係留意自己有興趣的書 <br />\n會限制左諗野同睇野的框架<br />\n所以大家有貨就拋 有興趣就搵來睇<br />\n未有興趣都可以知多啲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54c0dcd2f3b12f28353a93ef55e924243b8de19b","tid":8176,"uid":30900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T07:29:18.000Z","msg":"The Master and Margarita<br />\n經典，3個故事穿梭成本書，用種好荒謬瘋狂嘅手法去暗喻蘇聯時期嘅社會現象同mindset<br />\n個人特別鐘意Pilate嗰part，就文學上而言都寫得非常之靚<br />\n睇完你會覺得自己個腦好似坐完過山車咁<br />\n<br />\nI and Thou<br />\nMartin Buber寫嘅我個人認為非常適合入門讀者睇嘅existential哲學書，英文譯本順暢，用字淺白，雖然無論係Martin Buber定係本書嘅內文都經常摻入宗教意味，不過單純以哲學角度去睇都絕對係一本佳作<br />\n<br />\nThe Killer Angels<br />\nPulitzer Prize得獎作品，講美國南北戰爭，你唔需要有太多歷史底子都可以睇得好開心，敘述視角非常之好。喺外國係好多中學生都必讀嘅書嚟，我覺得香港啲學生都應該要讀，令你感受深嘅唔係打仗呢件事，而係當中每個人嘅抱負同理想，同埋what is humanity，what makes you a man"},{"pid":"260b71ef26861d41bbc989b273183ca4afa13ec0","tid":8176,"uid":30900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T07:34:21.000Z","msg":"休閒讀物畀多兩本<br />\n<br />\nThe Illustrated Man<br />\n由多個唔相關嘅小故事串連，方便啲大忙人可以自己揀想睇嘅chapter嚟睇。sci-fi嚟講可以話係天馬行空，淨係睇文字都可以睇到好刺激<br />\n<br />\nA Man Called Ove<br />\n呢本我推介咗畀個澳洲佬睇，係瑞典嘅小說嚟，比較平凡節奏亦都比較慢，好有瑞典嗰種淡味（如果你有睇過瑞典電影就會明我講乜），好似拍咗電影不過我冇睇啦，故事唔算係好驚喜好impressive，不過睇完都會有少少感觸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d17f0c2a246cfd60b7046c37f636a1874fb00fa2","tid":8176,"uid":73112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T07:35:13.000Z","msg":"武道狂之詩<br />\nD系列<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aa2f963c0266eaf17383b0f48478f4aed9d824d","tid":8176,"uid":30900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T07:45:41.000Z","msg":"仲有一本pale fire，合多文體於一身嘅書，如果你夠黐撚線不妨去挑戰吓<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">篇詩好撚靚</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}